// TerminalTabsContainer
// Desktop terminal container: tab bar + terminal content area for the current
// collab session. Coordinates tab management via useTerminalTabs and renders
// one EmbeddedTerminal per tab. Only the active tab is visible (display:flex
// vs display:none) to preserve xterm state. Triggers resize via double-RAF
// when the active tab changes.

FUNCTION TerminalTabsContainer(className) -> JSX                       EXPORT
  CALLS: TerminalTabBar (TerminalTabBar), EmbeddedTerminal (EmbeddedTerminal),
         useTerminalTabs (useTerminalTabs)
  Reads currentSession from sessionStore; derives project and session strings.
  Calls useTerminalTabs to get tabs, activeTabId, activeTab, and tab
  management callbacks.
  IF no session: shows "Select a session" placeholder.
  IF loading: shows "Loading terminals..." placeholder.
  IF error: shows error message.
  ELSE: renders TerminalTabBar + terminal content area.
  Terminal content: all tabs mounted, only active shown; uses EmbeddedTerminal
  per tab with memoized wsUrl config.
  On activeTabId change: dispatches a synthetic resize event on the wrapper
  element via double-RAF to trigger the ResizeObserver inside EmbeddedTerminal.
